OL,3,C'You feel violated': Exploring the
OL,4,Cdark world of tool theft
OL,6,FStephen Barker, a multi-trade from
OL,7,FHertfordshire, told me that he
OL,8,Fattempted to take his own life after
OL,9,F#15,000 worth of his tools were
OL,10,Fstolen, leaving him unable to work and
OL,11,Fspiraling into debt.
OL,13,F"It's not just a tool - it's a whole
OL,14,Fway of putting bread on the table for
OL,15,Four families, a whole way of buying
OL,16,Fschool shoes for our kids, a whole way
OL,17,Fof taking families on holidays and
OL,18,Fmaking magical moments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
