OL,6,F"People sit there and think 'oh it's
OL,7,Fjust a drill', but that drill earns me
OL,8,Fmoney to do what I've got to do.
OL,10,F"So when it's taken you 14 years to
OL,11,Fbuild up all your gear.... within five
OL,12,Fminutes you're gone, everything you've
OL,13,Fworked for - gone.
OL,15,F"You feel violated, you feel
OL,16,Fworthless."
