OL,3,C'You feel violated': Exploring the
OL,4,Cdark world of tool theft
OL,6,FA staggering 79% of tradespeople say
OL,7,Fthey've been victims at some point in
OL,8,Ftheir careers, and 65% believe the
OL,9,Fproblem is still getting worse.
OL,11,FIt's not just opportunistic thieves at
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,FMy investigation uncovered evidence
OL,15,Fthat rogue traders are using car boot
OL,16,Fsales to offload stolen tools in plain
OL,17,Fsight, often hiding valuable goods
OL,18,Finside vans or under stalls.
