OL,3,C'You feel violated': Exploring the
OL,4,Cdark world of tool theft
OL,6,FAt Willow Farm Boot sale in Essex, I
OL,7,Fjoined Metropolitan Police and Essex
OL,8,FPolice officers for an early morning
OL,9,Fraid: the two police forces' first
OL,10,Fattempt to work together to tackle the
OL,11,Ftool theft gangs.
OL,13,FDespite initially struggling to catch
OL,14,Fsellers red-handed - with many hiding
OL,15,Ftools in vehicles - the raid resulted
OL,16,Fin four arrests and the recovery of an
OL,17,Festimated #50,000 worth of stolen
OL,18,Fpower tools.
OL,20,F"It's a small win," once of the
OL,21,Fofficers on the raid told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
