OL,3,C'You feel violated': Exploring the
OL,4,Cdark world of tool theft
OL,6,FIn February 2025, hundreds of
OL,7,Ftradespeople, led by campaign group
OL,8,FTrades United, brought roads around
OL,9,FParliament to a standstill with a mass
OL,10,Fvan rally, sounding horns and
OL,11,Fdisplaying banners like "Hands off our
OL,12,Fvans" and "No tools, no trade."
OL,14,FOrganiser Shoaib Awan said up to 500
OL,15,Ftradespeople joined the demonstration,
OL,16,Fcalling for tougher sentencing for
OL,17,Ftool thieves, stronger policing, and a
OL,18,Fcrackdown on boot sales.
OL,20,FShoaib has led the charge to bring
OL,21,Fmore regulation at the boot sales.
