OL,6,FHe explained to ITV News that cheap
OL,7,Fprices make it easy to spot a
OL,8,Fsuspected stolen tool.
OL,10,F"How does that (tool) work out at #85
OL,11,Fwhen a tradesperson like myself will
OL,12,Fgo out into a shop and buy it for
OL,13,F#400?"
OL,15,F"Why would they sell brand new?", he
OL,16,Fasks me.
OL,18,F"And why would they have two of them?"
