OL,6,FThe rampant tool theft has made
OL,7,Ftradespeople spend money on expensive
OL,8,Fsecurity features and seen a rise in
OL,9,Finsurance premiums.
OL,11,FTradespeople told ITV News that those
OL,12,Fcosts are being passed on to customers.
OL,14,FA resolution at last?
OL,16,FTheir message was finally heard at the
OL,17,Fhighest level this week.
