OL,6,FAt Prime Minister's Questions, Amanda
OL,7,FMartin, MP for Portsmouth North,
OL,8,Fdirectly challenged Keir Starmer to
OL,9,Ftake urgent action.
OL,11,F"Tradespeople aren't just building
OL,12,FBritain, they're holding our
OL,13,Fcommunities together," she said.
OL,15,F"It's time we recognised the real cost
OL,16,Fof this crime and made the punishment
OL,17,Ffit the crime."
