OL,6,FAmanda Martin has become one of the
OL,7,Fmost vocal MPs on the issue since
OL,8,Fattending the Westminster rally
OL,9,Fearlier this year and introducing the
OL,10,FTheft of Tools of Trade (Sentencing)
OL,11,FBill, which will get its second
OL,12,Freading in Parliament later this year.
OL,14,FIn response, Keir Starmer - whose late
OL,15,Ffather worked as a toolmaker -
OL,16,Facknowledged the 'devastating impact'
OL,17,Fof tool theft, telling the Commons
OL,18,Fthat his government would address the
OL,19,Fproblem by:
