OL,6,FThe Prime Minister admitted that tool
OL,7,Ftheft can mean "thousands of pounds of
OL,8,Fwork lost, and with a huge impact to
OL,9,Fbusinesses and to families."
OL,11,FFor the tradespeople I spoke to, the
OL,12,Ffear is that unless boot sales face
OL,13,Fstricter checks, sentencing is
OL,14,Fstrengthened, and police are given the
OL,15,Fpowers to act swiftly, the tools of
OL,16,Ftheir trade will keep disappearing
OL,17,Finto the shadows `fueled by a
OL,18,Fcrimewave hiding in plain sight.
